videos.description: Colorado's D'Shawn Schwartz is left wide-open behind the 3-point line as he scores as time expires to upset No. 13 Dayton 78-76 in overtime.
videos.headline: Colorado's Schwartz hits buzzer-beating 3 to top Dayton in OT
